1
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,640
Now that the Glazed Frog

2
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,700
is back in the Tiger Marquis's hands,

3
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:49,000
just go and take it back.

4
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:15,000
Is this some kind of special training?

5
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,680
Luckily, I brought a secret weapon.

6
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,040
You didn't prepare this.

7
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,360
I modified the code.

8
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:20,160
And I taught the shooting.

9
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:20,960
Stop arguing.

10
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,720
It's a team effort.

11
00:02:59,120 --> 00:02:59,800
Your hidden weapon

12
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,520
doesn't seem to be working.

13
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:03,940
Professor,

14
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:04,680
what's going on?

15
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,040
It's broken.

16
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:06,680
In the underlying code of the virtual space,

17
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,520
there is no gunpowder.

18
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,580
Quick. Grappling.

19
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,280
A master.

20
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:15,020
Tiger Marquis is indeed a master.

21
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,200
Prince,

22
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:18,400
Tiger Marquis has passed your test.

23
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:21,060
You don't need to worry about my safety anymore.

24
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,660
Tiger Marquis,

25
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,480
you were a bit too heavy-handed.

26
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:27,760
What?

27
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,540
It doesn't hurt at all.

28
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,320
Prince,

29
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:35,040
why are you still standing there?

30
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:36,640
Won't you take a walk with me?

31
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:38,620
Coming.

32
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,160
Princess.

33
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:48,280
You said we're going to...

34
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,100
the Liuli Frog.

35
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,079
The Liuli Frog must have been

36
00:03:53,079 --> 00:03:54,680
hidden by the Tiger Marquis.

37
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,560
So, are we going to...

38
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,640
Is taking back one's own things

39
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,900
considered stealing?

40
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:01,840
Of course not.

41
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,000
Princess.

42
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,480
(in Thai) Aya,

43
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,290
exit the virtual space, quick!

44
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,519
Aya.

45
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,519
Aya.

46
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,160
Aya.

47
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,659
Professor Wei.

48
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,680
Liu Yu is in for some trouble.

49
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,360
I think the kid is quite capable.

50
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,080
Let him try.

51
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:49,480
How are you?

52
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,000
Wake up.

53
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,440
The Princess is gone.

54
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:55,760
Put me down.

55
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,160
Princess.

56
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:02,340
How did you just...

57
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,480
This isn't the place to talk.

58
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,120
Let's go.

59
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:34,600
I won't do anything

60
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,880
to harm you.

61
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:38,570
The Tiger Marquis is our common enemy.

62
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,240
I have never doubted you.

63
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,360
Marquis Hu is the most hardline pro-war faction

64
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,640
among the Great Ming nobles.

65
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:51,520
He earned his title through military merit.

66
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:52,920
For the Imperial Court to cease hostilities

67
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,120
and beat swords into plowshares

68
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:56,680
would be tantamount to ruining his bright future.

69
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:59,040
That is why he pushed for the marriage alliance.

70
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,700
No wonder he is so formidable.

71
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,480
The noble forces backing Marquis Hu

72
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,810
are unimaginably vast.

73
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,600
For the sake of the people of both lands,

74
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:08,360
my father championed the marriage alliance.

75
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,200
Although they originally

76
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:11,530
planned to block it at the court assembly,

77
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,720
they suddenly changed their minds.

78
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:14,800
For...

79
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,920
For...

80
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,240
the Tear of Buluotuo.

81
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,200
Exactly.

82
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:20,360
It was for this sacred relic of Siam.

83
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,580
And what about you?

84
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,720
Why did you agree to the marriage alliance?

85
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,680
I recall

86
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,680
that Siam and the Great Ming

87
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,760
are very far apart.

88
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:33,560
I also pushed for this alliance.

89
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,960
For the sake of the people.

90
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:39,720
For you.

91
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,850
Long time no see.

92
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:13,040
That Liuli Frog...

93
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,000
The Liuli Frog?

94
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,800
The Tiger Marquis sank it in the Li River.

95
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,440
Li.

96
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:20,680
The Princess said the Liuli Frog

97
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,880
is in the Li River.
